referenceAnswer:
Add `{ cache: 'no-store' }` to opt out of caching for user-specific (personalised) data:
```ts
const user = await fetch(`https://api.example.com/users/${params.id}`, {
  cache: 'no-store'
}).then(r => r.json());
```
Alternatively, reading `cookies()` or `headers()` in the same component automatically makes the route dynamic.

