referenceAnswer:
Export a matcher config to limit middleware to protected routes only:
```ts
export const config = {
  matcher: [
    '/((?!login|_next/static|_next/image|favicon.ico).*)'
  ]
};
```
This excludes the login page, Next.js internals, and static assets from the auth check.

